title: Obtain the Sinner
text: H-hi there... Minos Chief... Um, I... I'm the notorious cyclops of Eastside! ...No one would bully me if they hear this, right...?

title: Raise to Phase 1
text: My power got stronger? ...Sigh.

title: Raise to Phase 3
text: I'll try my best... to accept this power, and become... someone who can control it.

title: Level Start
text: Sigh... If only there were no battles.

title: Win Battles
text: A surprising victory...

title: Lose Battles
text: How... how scary... I-I'm really bad at fighting... I'm sorry... I'm sorry!

title: Ultimate Skill
text: Don't look at me... Stay away from me!

title: Die in Battles
text: I don't... want to... experience it again!

title: Greeting
text: Chief... I made some crafts today to give them to you. I hope you can be in a good mood all day...

title: Conversation 1
text: Um... These are all... photos that I took before... but I'm not great at taking photos of people. Huh? You want to take photos, too, Chief? ...I-I will try my best!

title: Conversation 2
text: Ch-chief... That was from before, when I was really nervous... I couldn't help but dig a hole in the room... I was thinking I could hide in it or something...

title: Conversation 3
text: Will Mommy and Daddy come to find me... I... I shouldn't think about it. I'll only cause them trouble...

title: Special Conversation 1
text: Huh...? Are there Eastsiders here, too?... They won't do anything out of line... right, Chief?

title: Special Conversation 2
text: It's filthy inside the sewers... but also very safe. There, I won't get chased by the FAC or bullied by others... That's why... I just stayed there and didn't come out...

title: Special Conversation 3
text: There's a lot of weird people here, but... everyone treats me well! No one shuns me because of my background, and no one complains about my smell... Some are even eager to model for my photos. It's really a novel experience...

title: Full Compliance
text: The world is so much clearer and prettier without my helmet... Thank you so much for giving me the courage to accept and control my power... I... I won't run away anymore! But... can I rely on you a bit more? I'm still not that great at fighting...

title: Idle
text: Hehe... I captured another amazing scene! Look, Chief... Ahh... Sorry... I'm a bit too excited...

title: Annoyed
text: Hey... ahhh! That... that... helmet is very dirty...

title: Special Attention
text: Um... right! Please don't... keep staring at me like that... It's making me nervous...

title: Dispatch
text: It's... not a dangerous mission, is it? ...No fighting involved, right?

title: Dispatch Complete
text: Ah... Thank goodness everything turned out fine...

title: Level Up
text: I'm fine the way I am! I... I don't need to get any stronger...

title: Join Team
text: There must be a better way to solve this than fighting, right?

title: Attire Obtained
text: Ah! Chief... I-I'm fine. I just... accidentally got entangled in the wires and fell down...

title: Greeting
text: Chief, you... want to hear me play it right now? But... I'm not, not ready yet... P-please, can you wait for the official performance? I'm still not good enough... I need to practice more!

title: Ordinary Contact 1
text: Can I... really do well on stage? Back in school, I used to watch the bands shine on stage, and I always thought they were so cool... Do you think... I could be like that too?

title: Ordinary Contact 2
text: ...My costumes for the performance are cute? Thank you! I made all the decorations myself by referring to comic books. I look quite like an idol in it, right? Hehehe ...

title: Idle
text: This guitar case is so fluffy... I think... it fits me just right... It feels like cuddling... so comfy... Zzz...

title: Annoyed
text: S-sorry! Could you please free me from this? ...Ah..! It's getting tighter...

title: Level Up
text: Hehehe... I'm getting better at this.

title: Special Attention
text: Ahhh... Please don't stare at me like that. I want to... wear my helmet again...
